### 1. 내가 진행중, 진행 완료한 미션을 모아서 보는 쿼리(페이징 포함)

<user> : id
<mission_request> : point, price, isSuccess
<store> : name

select u.id, m.point, m.price, m.isSuccess, s.name
from user as u 
join mission_request as m on u.id = user_id 
join store as s on s.id = user_id
where m.isSuccess = 1 and m.created_at <
(select created_at from m where id = 1)
order by m.created_at desc limit 10;

### 2. 리뷰작성하는 쿼리 (사진 배제)

<user> : id(join속성), name
<review> : user_id(join속성), detail, star

select u.name, r.detail, r.star, r.created_at
from user as u 
join review as r on u.id = r.user_id;

### 3. 홈 화면 쿼리( 페이징 포함)

<user> : id(join속성), address
<mission_request> : user_id(join속성), store_id(join속성), point, price, isSuccess, deadline
<store> : id(join속성), address(where절 조건), name

select u.address, m.point, m.price, m.deadline, s.name
from user as u 
join mission_request as m on u.id = m.user_id 
join store as s on m.store_id = s.id
where m.isSuccess = 0 and u.address = s.address and m.deadline not in
(select deadline
from mission_request
where deadline = 0)
and m.created_at <
(select created_at
from m
where id = 1)
order by m.created_at desc limit 10;

### 4. 마이 페이지 화면 쿼리

<user> : id로 모든정보 파악가능

select *
from user u
